* {{cite book |last1=Pobee |first1=John S. |title=Persecution and Martyrdom in the Theology of Paul |date=1985 |publisher=Bloomsbury |location=New York |isbn=9780905774534 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RmqKMQEACAAJ |language=en}}
